1
00:00:06,122 --> 00:00:08,547
♫ I want to go to the future ♫

2
00:00:08,547 --> 00:00:12,202
♫  Time bears witness to my quirkiness  ♫

3
00:00:12,202 --> 00:00:18,295
♫ I want to seize the day and put the whole world into my head ♫

4
00:00:18,295 --> 00:00:24,521
♫ I want to go back in time to do all the crazy things I didn't do ♫

5
00:00:24,521 --> 00:00:30,742
♫  Don't say goodbye, don't be in a daze, let my radiant light be bright  ♫

6
00:00:30,742 --> 00:00:36,028
♫ We are always looking forward to the unknown future ♫

7
00:00:36,028 --> 00:00:43,128
♫  And often overlooking our surroundings and best plan in front of us  ♫

8
00:00:43,128 --> 00:00:48,352
♫ Every day my heart beats for you ♫

9
00:00:48,352 --> 00:00:49,965
♫ Be your light ♫

10
00:00:49,965 --> 00:00:55,528
♫  You are no doubt irreplaceable  ♫

11
00:00:55,528 --> 00:01:02,128
♫ Every day the sun shines through the window ♫

12
00:01:02,128 --> 00:01:08,495
♫ With the reflection of you being my incredible highlight ♫

13
00:01:08,495 --> 00:01:11,802
[I Don't Want to be Brothers with You]

14
00:01:12,370 --> 00:01:14,560
I'm opening it?

15
00:01:19,230 --> 00:01:22,000
W-What do you think? Are you happy with it?

16
00:01:22,000 --> 00:01:23,940
I'm very happy!

17
00:01:33,540 --> 00:01:37,619
Dad didn't come back to celebrate my birthday. He missed so many highlights.

18
00:01:37,619 --> 00:01:42,620
I had a wonderful time anyway. I've outdone myself and celebrated in style.

19
00:01:42,620 --> 00:01:44,599
Let him regret it!

20
00:01:56,300 --> 00:02:00,100
Jia, your dad will surely come back soon. Really.

21
00:02:00,100 --> 00:02:01,339
Beibei,

22
00:02:01,339 --> 00:02:06,119
I think my dad a-already came back.

23
00:02:06,119 --> 00:02:08,779
That's a good thing. Where is he?

24
00:02:08,779 --> 00:02:10,180
I have no idea.

25
00:02:10,180 --> 00:02:14,180
He just called the house a few times a-and didn't say anything.

26
00:02:14,180 --> 00:02:16,580
Auntie told me to wait for a bit longer.

27
00:02:16,580 --> 00:02:18,580
Do you think

28
00:02:18,580 --> 00:02:21,340
h-he doesn't want to see me?

29
00:02:21,340 --> 00:02:24,459
That's not possible, Jia. You're so awesome.

30
00:02:24,459 --> 00:02:28,780
There's no way he doesn't want to see you. He's probably just too embarrassed

31
00:02:28,780 --> 00:02:29,980
and afraid you'll blame him.

32
00:02:29,980 --> 00:02:35,979
- That's right.
- I-I don't blame him. I-I-I just want to see him.

33
00:02:41,860 --> 00:02:44,480
W-What are you doing?

34
00:02:48,759 --> 00:02:50,379
I changed my birthday wish.

35
00:02:50,379 --> 00:02:53,219
I wish Jia can see her dad soon.

36
00:02:53,219 --> 00:02:56,640
D-Don't do that, Beibei. Well... what about your wish?

37
00:02:56,640 --> 00:02:57,721
It's okay.

38
00:02:57,721 --> 00:03:00,899
At first, I just wanted my dad to celebrate my birthday with me.

39
00:03:00,899 --> 00:03:03,659
But now, I think it's more important that you get to see your dad.

40
00:03:03,659 --> 00:03:08,719
Besides, I have you guys now. I have so many gifts now.

41
00:03:12,339 --> 00:03:14,900
What do you think is wrong with Zhao Jiabao?

42
00:03:14,900 --> 00:03:18,760
Why did he give me a pen? That doesn't go with my style at all.

43
00:03:20,539 --> 00:03:21,980
It's not a simple gift.

44
00:03:21,980 --> 00:03:24,320
I know. It's pure gold.

45
00:03:25,379 --> 00:03:27,381
No,

46
00:03:27,381 --> 00:03:32,939
look, the card says headphones. But he gave you a pen instead.

47
00:03:32,939 --> 00:03:34,700
He just said he made a mistake.

48
00:03:34,700 --> 00:03:36,099
What if he didn't?

49
00:03:36,099 --> 00:03:41,080
What if he wanted to give you headphones but ended up giving you a pen?

50
00:03:42,626 --> 00:03:43,580
So what?

51
00:03:43,580 --> 00:03:48,080
By changing the present, that means he takes your birthday gift seriously.

52
00:03:48,080 --> 00:03:53,299
When a boy cares so much about a girl's birthday,

53
00:03:53,860 --> 00:03:56,020
what does that mean?

54
00:04:02,020 --> 00:04:03,779
That's impossible.

55
00:04:03,779 --> 00:04:09,599
You know Zhao Jiabao always bullies me in class. He mocks me all the time.

56
00:04:09,599 --> 00:04:12,659
But Jiabao never mocks other girls.

57
00:04:12,659 --> 00:04:15,119
Exactly.

58
00:04:15,119 --> 00:04:18,879
That's because he never sees me as a girl.

59
00:04:18,879 --> 00:04:24,059
There's more. The song he just sang seems to mean something.

60
00:04:24,059 --> 00:04:28,459
Seems like there's someone in his heart.

61
00:04:35,730 --> 00:04:36,580
Who is it?

62
00:04:36,580 --> 00:04:38,580
Beibei, can you come out here for a second?

63
00:04:38,580 --> 00:04:40,219
Jiabao.

64
00:04:40,219 --> 00:04:41,519
What do you want?

65
00:04:41,519 --> 00:04:44,480
Come out here. I have something to tell you.

66
00:04:45,040 --> 00:04:46,199
Go.

67
00:04:46,199 --> 00:04:48,219
Go on.

68
00:04:48,219 --> 00:04:49,940
Listen to what he says. Go on.

69
00:04:49,940 --> 00:04:51,819
I'll go then.

70
00:04:53,140 --> 00:04:54,859
Hurry, hurry.

71
00:04:54,859 --> 00:04:57,120
I will reject him.

72
00:05:10,850 --> 00:05:12,559
What did you want to say?

73
00:05:12,559 --> 00:05:15,920
Beibei, close your eyes.

74
00:05:19,060 --> 00:05:20,960
He's shy.

75
00:05:24,620 --> 00:05:27,620
Beibei, happy birthday.

76
00:05:27,620 --> 00:05:29,679
How's that? Are you happy?

77
00:05:29,679 --> 00:05:32,160
Zhao Jiabao!

78
00:05:32,160 --> 00:05:34,474
- Zhao Jiabao!
- What are you doing?

79
00:05:37,160 --> 00:05:38,279
Meng!

80
00:05:38,279 --> 00:05:39,319
What's wrong?

81
00:05:39,319 --> 00:05:41,500
My eyes hurt!

82
00:05:51,199 --> 00:05:53,199
I'm sorry.

83
00:05:53,199 --> 00:05:56,800
If apologies work, why would we need the police?

84
00:06:33,920 --> 00:06:35,339
Hello.

85
00:06:35,339 --> 00:06:38,920
Beibei, come to the hospital now. Your dad is having surgery!

86
00:06:56,360 --> 00:07:00,362
[Episode 22: Deceive Tears with a Smile]

87
00:07:09,550 --> 00:07:11,580
[Operating Room]

88
00:07:13,730 --> 00:07:17,020
Mom, what happened to my dad?

89
00:07:25,770 --> 00:07:28,480
Say something, Mom!

90
00:07:31,480 --> 00:07:33,190
What happened?

91
00:07:37,330 --> 00:07:40,859
Jin is having a minor surgery.

92
00:07:40,859 --> 00:07:45,199
The doctor said there was a problem with his heart. He needs a heart transplant.

93
00:07:46,840 --> 00:07:48,553
No,

94
00:07:49,219 --> 00:07:51,779
it's a cardiac valve replacement surgery.

95
00:07:51,779 --> 00:07:54,460
The surgery has a very minimal risk, only 4%.

96
00:07:54,460 --> 00:07:56,199
It's a very minor surgery.

97
00:07:56,199 --> 00:08:00,440
The doctor said it should be fine since he passed out in the hospital.

98
00:08:00,440 --> 00:08:02,980
I thought it should be fine too.

99
00:08:02,980 --> 00:08:06,901
But why did Jin... have massive bleeding halfway through the surgery?

100
00:08:06,901 --> 00:08:09,157
They are still conducting emergency rescue procedures.

101
00:08:28,050 --> 00:08:31,320
[Tieyuan Municipal Hospital]

102
00:08:31,320 --> 00:08:35,570
[Anesthesiology Dept. | Operating Room]

103
00:10:02,317 --> 00:10:06,580
Doudou, daddy will be all right.

104
00:10:06,580 --> 00:10:08,670
Don't be scared.

105
00:10:08,670 --> 00:10:11,740
Here, help me wipe too.

106
00:10:33,570 --> 00:10:39,180
Doudou, be a good boy, go buy some drinks for mom and Uncle Gao, okay?

107
00:10:42,340 --> 00:10:45,059
Doudou, I'll go with you.

108
00:10:49,459 --> 00:10:54,400
Uncle Gao, we've bothered you for so long. Go home and get some rest.

109
00:10:54,400 --> 00:10:59,719
It's okay. I'm not tired. Besides, you need the help of an adult here.

110
00:11:00,419 --> 00:11:04,400
I'm already seventeen. I'm almost an adult.

111
00:11:06,100 --> 00:11:09,800
All right, don't hang around here. Go home and get some rest.

112
00:11:09,800 --> 00:11:12,699
B-But Beibei, Principal Jin...

113
00:11:12,699 --> 00:11:14,679
My dad will be all right.

114
00:11:14,679 --> 00:11:18,979
If you don't go home, your family will worry. Go now.

115
00:11:20,695 --> 00:11:21,740
Listen to me.

116
00:11:21,740 --> 00:11:22,819
- Come on, Gao Yang.
- Beibei,

117
00:11:22,819 --> 00:11:24,659
- Jiabao,
- we should stay here with you.

118
00:11:24,659 --> 00:11:28,360
That's not necessary. Go, go. Go home now.

119
00:11:28,360 --> 00:11:30,900
You two are in charge of taking the girls home.

120
00:11:30,900 --> 00:11:33,459
Beibei, we should stay here with you.

121
00:11:33,459 --> 00:11:36,400
No, I don't need that.

122
00:11:36,819 --> 00:11:39,380
All right, go home now.

123
00:11:40,860 --> 00:11:43,859
Why are you all looking at me?

124
00:11:43,859 --> 00:11:47,380
My dad will be fine. Nothing will happen to him.

125
00:11:47,380 --> 00:11:49,335
Say no more, Beibei.

126
00:11:49,335 --> 00:11:51,838
- We'll all wait here with you.
- That's right.

127
00:11:52,439 --> 00:11:54,980
W-W-We'll wait here with you.

128
00:11:54,980 --> 00:12:00,340
No, I'll be angry if you don't leave. Today is my birthday. You have to listen to me.

129
00:12:00,340 --> 00:12:02,819
Beibei, you can't handle this alone.

130
00:12:02,819 --> 00:12:06,839
Who said I can't? Besides, I'm not alone.

131
00:12:06,839 --> 00:12:11,759
My mom and Doudou are here. I have to take care of them too.

132
00:12:12,459 --> 00:12:14,496
I must be able to handle it.

133
00:12:16,740 --> 00:12:20,559
Jia, what's wrong? Why are you crying?

134
00:12:20,559 --> 00:12:22,207
Jia.

135
00:12:24,500 --> 00:12:25,979
Beibei,

136
00:12:25,979 --> 00:12:30,219
I won't see my dad anymore.

137
00:12:30,219 --> 00:12:33,380
I give your wish back.

138
00:12:34,260 --> 00:12:37,660
What are you saying, Silly? I'll be okay.

139
00:12:37,660 --> 00:12:39,539
Don't worry.

140
00:12:40,039 --> 00:12:44,339
We'll all be fine. Don't cry, Silly.

141
00:12:53,500 --> 00:12:55,600
Jin Libin's family.

142
00:12:56,779 --> 00:12:58,340
Here.

143
00:12:58,340 --> 00:13:01,629
The operation was successful. Please go through the hospitalization procedures.

144
00:13:04,060 --> 00:13:05,170
- Thank you, Doctor.
- Thank you.

145
00:13:05,170 --> 00:13:06,560
Everything's fine.

146
00:13:06,560 --> 00:13:08,900
Sister-in-law, Jin is okay. Jin is okay.

147
00:13:08,900 --> 00:13:11,879
Beibei, the operation was successful!

148
00:13:11,879 --> 00:13:13,539
Old Jin is fine!

149
00:13:13,539 --> 00:13:18,380
Beibei, did you hear that? The operation was successful, Beibei!

150
00:13:20,919 --> 00:13:21,860
It was successful.

151
00:13:21,860 --> 00:13:23,786
It was successful.

152
00:13:29,220 --> 00:13:32,259
Wait, the operation was successful. Why are you crying?

153
00:13:32,259 --> 00:13:35,359
I was so worried.

154
00:13:37,430 --> 00:13:39,379
It was a false alarm.

155
00:13:43,000 --> 00:13:45,399
Daddy is okay.

156
00:13:45,399 --> 00:13:49,880
I'll never celebrate my birthday again.

157
00:14:02,400 --> 00:14:04,499
What's wrong, Doudou?

158
00:14:04,860 --> 00:14:06,959
Are you hungry?

159
00:14:10,100 --> 00:14:12,660
It's noon already. I'll go make you some food.

160
00:14:12,660 --> 00:14:15,740
Yes, Xiaowen will make you what you want.

161
00:14:17,299 --> 00:14:18,890
What's wrong?

162
00:14:19,579 --> 00:14:21,359
Why aren't you speaking?

163
00:14:33,122 --> 00:14:35,802
[Notice of Payment]

164
00:14:38,690 --> 00:14:41,898
- Sister-in-law, eat something.
- Bin,

165
00:14:42,699 --> 00:14:45,499
thank you. I'll eat it later.

166
00:14:45,499 --> 00:14:47,117
Do you have enough money?

167
00:14:47,659 --> 00:14:50,260
Yes, yes.

168
00:14:52,430 --> 00:14:54,148
Take this.

169
00:14:54,860 --> 00:14:59,159
Bin, what's this for? I told you I have enough money.

170
00:14:59,159 --> 00:15:02,099
Sister-in-law, I am very familiar with hospitalization.

171
00:15:02,099 --> 00:15:06,220
When Gao Yang's grandparents were in the hospital, I never knew when I would need money.

172
00:15:06,220 --> 00:15:09,380
Just save it for a rainy day.

173
00:15:13,860 --> 00:15:16,779
All right, I'll take it for now.

174
00:15:16,779 --> 00:15:19,459
After he's discharged from the hospital, I'll withdraw money from the bank and pay you back.

175
00:15:19,459 --> 00:15:25,239
Our families are so close. Besides, Jin Doudou is staying at my place. You can't escape.

176
00:15:26,340 --> 00:15:27,900
All right, I'll go check on Old Jin.

177
00:15:27,900 --> 00:15:29,839
Beibei is in there.

178
00:15:31,030 --> 00:15:34,020
Beibei is really reliable now.

179
00:15:34,020 --> 00:15:36,260
She didn't complain at all when she was handling things with us.

180
00:15:36,260 --> 00:15:38,220
I didn't know she had it in her.

181
00:15:38,220 --> 00:15:40,120
Tell me about it.

182
00:15:40,120 --> 00:15:43,839
I always thought Beibei would be hard to handle,

183
00:15:43,839 --> 00:15:47,040
but I didn't expect her to be like this.

184
00:15:47,459 --> 00:15:49,619
That child,

185
00:15:49,619 --> 00:15:54,000
after years of reprimanding,

186
00:15:54,000 --> 00:15:56,620
suddenly, she just grew up

187
00:15:57,059 --> 00:15:59,300
one day.

188
00:16:05,220 --> 00:16:07,260
I really envy you.

189
00:16:08,100 --> 00:16:13,924
My boy Gao Yang, I've done everything I could with him, when will he ever grow up?

190
00:16:13,924 --> 00:16:16,479
He will someday.

191
00:16:18,290 --> 00:16:19,020
Thank you.

192
00:16:19,020 --> 00:16:22,719
Come on, Sister-in-law, eat something first. Don't thank me.

193
00:17:24,930 --> 00:17:28,919
Dad, you're awake?

194
00:17:32,380 --> 00:17:34,600
Why are you here?

195
00:17:34,600 --> 00:17:39,000
You had excessive bleeding during your surgery last night.

196
00:17:39,000 --> 00:17:41,280
You really scared me.

197
00:17:44,540 --> 00:17:48,400
Are you thirsty? I'll pour you some water.

198
00:18:01,210 --> 00:18:02,673
Dad.

199
00:18:15,580 --> 00:18:17,303
Okay.

200
00:18:20,100 --> 00:18:23,680
How do you feel, Dad? Does it still hurt?

201
00:18:23,680 --> 00:18:27,140
I'm okay. I feel much better.

202
00:18:29,310 --> 00:18:31,198
Where's Doudou?

203
00:18:32,060 --> 00:18:34,740
He's at Uncle Gao's place.

204
00:18:34,740 --> 00:18:37,712
Why do you ask about Doudou as soon as you wake up?

205
00:18:37,712 --> 00:18:40,820
What date is today?

206
00:18:40,820 --> 00:18:42,390
It's the ninth.

207
00:18:49,860 --> 00:18:55,719
Hurry, there's a notebook in the bag over there.

208
00:19:03,780 --> 00:19:07,480
This is for you.

209
00:19:11,259 --> 00:19:16,119
I understand, Dad. I will study hard.

210
00:19:18,279 --> 00:19:20,460
Open it.

211
00:19:30,960 --> 00:19:32,622
Dad,

212
00:19:33,440 --> 00:19:36,079
there are so many signatures on it.

213
00:19:36,680 --> 00:19:38,960
Happy birthday.

214
00:19:39,739 --> 00:19:41,550
I...

215
00:19:42,080 --> 00:19:43,887
didn't forget.

216
00:19:45,900 --> 00:19:51,580
Daddy, I will never celebrate my birthday again.

217
00:19:51,580 --> 00:19:55,880
Your health is more important than anything.

218
00:19:57,459 --> 00:20:01,171
From now on, I will spend all your birthdays

219
00:20:02,880 --> 00:20:05,259
with you.

220
00:20:07,240 --> 00:20:09,600
Dad!

221
00:20:12,259 --> 00:20:14,919
Doudou, eat some meat.

222
00:20:16,219 --> 00:20:18,899
Eat some vegetables Doudou. Eat more vegetables.

223
00:20:18,899 --> 00:20:21,459
That's right. You should go on a diet.

224
00:20:31,280 --> 00:20:34,000
Doudou, you're not hungry?

225
00:20:34,499 --> 00:20:36,780
Are you feeling any discomfort?

226
00:20:40,300 --> 00:20:42,199
What happened to him?

227
00:20:42,199 --> 00:20:46,279
Did his dad's surgery scare him?

228
00:20:50,380 --> 00:20:53,580
Doudou, your dad is all right.

229
00:20:53,580 --> 00:20:56,760
He's just going to stay in the hospital for a few days. He'll come back soon.

230
00:20:56,760 --> 00:20:57,759
That's right.

231
00:20:57,759 --> 00:21:02,180
Look, your mom, your sister, and Mr. Gao are all staying in the hospital with your dad.

232
00:21:02,180 --> 00:21:03,499
Don't worry.

233
00:21:03,499 --> 00:21:08,540
We'll babysit you for a few days. You can tell us everything, okay?

234
00:21:12,119 --> 00:21:13,659
Is he depressed?

235
00:21:13,659 --> 00:21:15,939
No way, Doudou is so young.

236
00:21:15,939 --> 00:21:20,680
You have no idea. I was just like Doudou when Gao Bin and my mom got a divorce.

237
00:21:20,680 --> 00:21:23,079
I didn't talk for weeks.

238
00:21:24,394 --> 00:21:26,799
What happened then? How did you take care of it?

239
00:21:26,810 --> 00:21:28,310
I'm not passing you.

240
00:21:28,310 --> 00:21:29,510
Sakuragi!

241
00:21:29,519 --> 00:21:31,980
Miyagi, please!

242
00:21:35,180 --> 00:21:38,480
Miyagi, why did you do that?

243
00:21:48,060 --> 00:21:50,999
Doudou, do you like it? What do you think?

244
00:21:53,860 --> 00:21:55,060
Rukawa Kaede is awesome after all.

245
00:21:55,060 --> 00:21:58,320
Sakuragi, help me pass the ball to Rukawa Kaede.

246
00:21:58,320 --> 00:21:59,820
He's fine now.

247
00:21:59,820 --> 00:22:01,739
He's getting better and better.

248
00:22:01,739 --> 00:22:04,100
Well, what does Doudou usually like to eat?

249
00:22:04,100 --> 00:22:06,282
What does Doudou like to eat?

250
00:22:06,282 --> 00:22:08,599
What's wrong with him? Is he acting up again?

251
00:22:08,599 --> 00:22:11,100
No, no. No, he's been behaving.

252
00:22:11,100 --> 00:22:13,959
Don't worry. We just want to reward him.

253
00:22:13,959 --> 00:22:15,751
That's more like it.

254
00:22:16,259 --> 00:22:20,580
Doudou likes sweet and cold treats, like popsicles and such.

255
00:22:20,580 --> 00:22:23,521
But don't give him so much or he'll have diarrhea.

256
00:22:40,219 --> 00:22:42,200
What's wrong with Doudou?

257
00:22:42,200 --> 00:22:47,140
Doudou is fine. Gao Yang said he's been behaving. He wants to reward him with some treats.

258
00:22:48,620 --> 00:22:52,719
Dad, you should sleep for a while. I'll go get your medicine.

259
00:22:54,459 --> 00:22:56,208
I'm leaving now.

260
00:23:00,499 --> 00:23:03,019
Doudou, you can have all of these today.

261
00:23:03,019 --> 00:23:05,359
You can eat whichever one you want.

262
00:23:10,660 --> 00:23:13,000
Eat this first. This is really tasty.

263
00:23:13,000 --> 00:23:17,319
I'm telling you, the chocolate one is really yummy. Come on.

264
00:23:20,459 --> 00:23:22,051
What do you think?

265
00:23:26,659 --> 00:23:28,166
What happened?

266
00:23:29,419 --> 00:23:32,839
What does that mean? This doesn't taste good?

267
00:23:34,459 --> 00:23:36,165
It's fine.

268
00:23:36,540 --> 00:23:39,280
Oh, no, he's really depressed.

269
00:23:40,939 --> 00:23:46,140
I never thought Doudou would be so sensitive at such a young age.

270
00:23:54,340 --> 00:23:55,780
Look, you'll smell nice.

271
00:23:55,780 --> 00:23:57,459
Come on, Doudou. Brush your teeth.

272
00:23:57,459 --> 00:23:59,137
Yes, brush your teeth.

273
00:24:01,179 --> 00:24:03,599
You have to brush your teeth before you sleep.

274
00:24:07,490 --> 00:24:10,719
Doudou, I know you're really upset now,

275
00:24:10,719 --> 00:24:12,620
but you still have to brush your teeth,

276
00:24:12,620 --> 00:24:16,479
because from now on until you get old, you'll only get one set of teeth.

277
00:24:16,479 --> 00:24:21,059
If you don't protect it, you'll regret it for the rest of your life.

278
00:24:23,000 --> 00:24:25,079
Don't scare him.

279
00:24:26,659 --> 00:24:29,499
Filling a tooth is very expensive.

280
00:24:29,499 --> 00:24:33,919
That's what I told Mi Jia when she didn't like to brush her teeth back then.

281
00:24:33,919 --> 00:24:35,820
- Come on, brush your teeth.
- Doudou, come on, brush your teeth.

282
00:24:35,820 --> 00:24:37,839
Come on, Doudou. I'll brush them for you.

283
00:24:37,839 --> 00:24:40,060
- What's wrong? I'll help you brush them.
- Open your mouth.

284
00:24:40,060 --> 00:24:41,699
You have to brush your teeth.

285
00:24:41,699 --> 00:24:42,900
What's going on here?

286
00:24:42,900 --> 00:24:45,860
Doudou won't brush his teeth.

287
00:24:46,140 --> 00:24:50,739
He's probably upset about Principal Jin staying in the hospital. He hasn't spoken all day.

288
00:24:55,730 --> 00:24:57,171
Doudou,

289
00:24:57,680 --> 00:24:59,823
open your mouth for Uncle Gao.

290
00:25:08,459 --> 00:25:09,820
You have cavities.

291
00:25:09,820 --> 00:25:12,419
We'll take you to get it fixed tomorrow.

292
00:25:12,419 --> 00:25:15,734
I still have to go take care of Old Jin at the hospital. I'm going to bed.

293
00:25:20,760 --> 00:25:24,119
Xiaowen, how would they fill a tooth?

294
00:25:25,019 --> 00:25:27,780
The book said the doctor will use a drill

295
00:25:27,780 --> 00:25:30,760
to grind away the bad tooth little by little.

296
00:25:30,760 --> 00:25:35,400
If it's badly decayed, they have to kill the nerve first

297
00:25:35,900 --> 00:25:37,599
and do a root canal.

298
00:25:37,599 --> 00:25:39,060
That would hurt so much.

299
00:25:39,060 --> 00:25:41,528
They would give you anesthesia, right?

300
00:25:41,528 --> 00:25:43,462
That depends.

301
00:25:43,462 --> 00:25:45,459
Sometimes they don't give you anesthesia.

302
00:25:45,459 --> 00:25:47,207
You just have to bear with the pain.

303
00:25:52,860 --> 00:25:56,820
Doudou, the book isn't always right.

304
00:25:56,820 --> 00:25:59,760
Don't be scared. We'll be with you.

305
00:25:59,760 --> 00:26:01,179
Don't worry, let's go.

306
00:26:01,179 --> 00:26:02,610
Let's go.

307
00:26:16,360 --> 00:26:19,900
Xiaowen, I think Doudou seems scared.

308
00:26:19,900 --> 00:26:21,499
You should hold him down later.

309
00:26:21,499 --> 00:26:24,759
Don't worry. The hospital has special chairs for children.

310
00:26:24,759 --> 00:26:26,236
They will tie him down.

311
00:26:29,660 --> 00:26:31,019
Where is he?

312
00:26:31,019 --> 00:26:33,299
- Doudou!
- Doudou!

313
00:26:33,860 --> 00:26:34,979
Doudou!

314
00:26:34,979 --> 00:26:35,979
Doudou!

315
00:26:35,979 --> 00:26:37,655
Open the door, Sir!

316
00:26:44,680 --> 00:26:47,199
Doudou!

317
00:26:49,879 --> 00:26:52,174
Doudou!

318
00:26:55,659 --> 00:26:57,800
Your cue isn't straight.

319
00:26:58,140 --> 00:26:59,621
Let me see.

320
00:27:02,019 --> 00:27:03,929
I'll get you another one, Sir.

321
00:27:05,780 --> 00:27:07,499
You guys go ahead.

322
00:27:09,060 --> 00:27:12,779
Boss, he said this cue isn't straight.

323
00:27:12,779 --> 00:27:14,340
Just ignore him.

324
00:27:14,340 --> 00:27:16,000
He's looking for trouble.

325
00:27:20,419 --> 00:27:23,340
How did you do on the college entrance exam? Are the scores published yet?

326
00:27:23,340 --> 00:27:24,869
Yes.

327
00:27:26,000 --> 00:27:27,955
You didn't do well, right?

328
00:27:32,575 --> 00:27:37,439
You're only nineteen. Working here for me isn't a long-term solution.

329
00:27:37,900 --> 00:27:41,450
You... You should find a real job.

330
00:27:41,450 --> 00:27:43,299
Come on, set the balls.

331
00:27:43,299 --> 00:27:44,840
Coming.

332
00:27:50,880 --> 00:27:52,759
Doudou!

333
00:27:52,759 --> 00:27:55,300
- Doudou!
- Doudou, don't run!

334
00:27:56,499 --> 00:27:57,680
Doudou!

335
00:27:57,680 --> 00:28:00,620
Oh, God! Why are you in such a rush? What are you doing?

336
00:28:00,620 --> 00:28:02,499
I'm sorry. Our brother ran away. I'm sorry! I'm sorry!

337
00:28:02,499 --> 00:28:05,139
Be careful next time! Don't be careless.

338
00:28:08,060 --> 00:28:09,660
Doudou!

339
00:28:09,660 --> 00:28:11,459
Doudou!

340
00:28:15,079 --> 00:28:17,040
Doudou!

341
00:28:31,780 --> 00:28:33,060
Have you see him?

342
00:28:33,060 --> 00:28:34,662
No.

343
00:28:44,699 --> 00:28:46,019
Where did this little boy come from?

344
00:28:46,019 --> 00:28:47,219
Let go of me!

345
00:28:47,219 --> 00:28:48,320
Are you asking for a beating?

346
00:28:48,320 --> 00:28:49,900
Bro,

347
00:28:49,900 --> 00:28:51,979
- I'm sorry.
- Is this your child?

348
00:28:51,979 --> 00:28:54,060
Does he need to be disciplined?

349
00:28:54,060 --> 00:28:55,860
What are you doing?

350
00:28:55,860 --> 00:28:57,620
He's just a child.

351
00:28:57,939 --> 00:28:59,000
Don't take him seriously.

352
00:28:59,000 --> 00:29:01,340
What kind of billiard room is this? Anyone can come here?

353
00:29:01,340 --> 00:29:04,899
If you won't let me teach him a lesson, I'll teach you a lesson.

354
00:29:07,380 --> 00:29:08,786
Come on.

355
00:29:09,219 --> 00:29:11,299
Don't you want to teach me a lesson?

356
00:29:12,979 --> 00:29:14,495
All right,

357
00:29:15,640 --> 00:29:18,060
just you wait. Let's go!

358
00:29:21,979 --> 00:29:23,820
Where are you going? Where are your parents?

359
00:29:23,820 --> 00:29:24,839
Let go!

360
00:29:24,839 --> 00:29:26,620
Children shouldn't run out on their own, understand?

361
00:29:26,620 --> 00:29:29,179
Let go! I'll smack you!

362
00:29:29,179 --> 00:29:31,140
You want to smack me?

363
00:29:31,140 --> 00:29:34,900
Do you know Gao Yang from No.3 High School? That's my little buddy!

364
00:29:35,659 --> 00:29:37,444
Gao Yang?

365
00:29:37,444 --> 00:29:40,580
Damn Doudou, why is he still so naughty in such a critical time?

366
00:29:40,580 --> 00:29:43,019
I'll smack him once we find him.

367
00:29:43,019 --> 00:29:44,459
Let's check the market again.

368
00:29:44,459 --> 00:29:46,839
Let's go find your parent. Hurry.

369
00:29:48,380 --> 00:29:51,319
Dong Dawei, let go of my little brother!

370
00:29:51,699 --> 00:29:53,147
Go on.

371
00:29:54,380 --> 00:29:55,699
Isn't Gao Yang your little buddy?

372
00:29:55,699 --> 00:29:57,259
What are you afraid of?

373
00:29:57,259 --> 00:29:59,760
If you have any problems, come at me.

374
00:30:02,301 --> 00:30:05,180
I didn't bully him. You can ask him yourself if he wants to go with you.

375
00:30:05,180 --> 00:30:07,620
I'm not going. I don't want to fill my teeth!

376
00:30:07,620 --> 00:30:09,519
What's so bad about filling your teeth? Come over here!

377
00:30:09,519 --> 00:30:11,500
Doudou, Doudou, look at me.

378
00:30:11,500 --> 00:30:13,540
If you don't do it today, it'll hurt worse tomorrow.

379
00:30:13,540 --> 00:30:16,580
I don't want to! I don't want excessive bleeding!

380
00:30:16,580 --> 00:30:18,060
You won't have excessive bleeding from filling your teeth.

381
00:30:18,060 --> 00:30:20,620
I don't believe you! My dad had excessive bleeding!

382
00:30:20,620 --> 00:30:23,060
Trust me. Teeth fillings won't hurt.

383
00:30:23,060 --> 00:30:26,780
How can you say that? Have you done it before?

384
00:30:27,460 --> 00:30:30,000
Little Man, look at this.

385
00:30:32,148 --> 00:30:33,580
I filled my teeth before.

386
00:30:33,580 --> 00:30:34,605
I'm still alive, right?

387
00:30:34,605 --> 00:30:36,259
Does it hurt?

388
00:30:36,259 --> 00:30:40,480
If you can't even stand that pain, how will you be a man?

389
00:30:46,170 --> 00:30:47,350
[22 Casual Beer House]

390
00:30:47,350 --> 00:30:50,300
[Barbeque]

391
00:31:02,459 --> 00:31:04,380
Is the little man okay?

392
00:31:04,380 --> 00:31:07,659
He's fine. My dad is watching over him at home.

393
00:31:07,659 --> 00:31:09,149
Dawei,

394
00:31:09,580 --> 00:31:11,326
thank you for that today.

395
00:31:13,300 --> 00:31:15,780
Exactly, you've been a great help.

396
00:31:15,780 --> 00:31:18,019
This meal is on us.

397
00:31:18,580 --> 00:31:20,259
You're just a student. Don't try to show off.

398
00:31:20,259 --> 00:31:23,119
I'm already working now. Let the rich man pay.

399
00:31:29,010 --> 00:31:30,620
Why are you working?

400
00:31:30,620 --> 00:31:32,079
You're not going to school anymore?

401
00:31:32,079 --> 00:31:34,800
What's so great about school? It's good to start working earlier.

402
00:31:34,800 --> 00:31:36,675
You didn't do well on the exam?

403
00:31:37,259 --> 00:31:38,860
It's all your fault for being a doomsayer.

404
00:31:38,860 --> 00:31:40,600
No, I...

405
00:31:40,600 --> 00:31:41,680
Just kidding.

406
00:31:41,680 --> 00:31:44,179
I haven't studied for years. How could I get a good score?

407
00:31:44,179 --> 00:31:47,739
It's an accident if I do well on the exam. It's only natural that I don't do well.

408
00:31:47,739 --> 00:31:49,540
It has nothing to do with you.

409
00:31:50,340 --> 00:31:52,970
Well, what are you doing now?

410
00:31:55,140 --> 00:31:57,509
I'm in business with a few friends.

411
00:31:57,509 --> 00:32:00,739
Dawei, the shipment is here. Go unload it now.

412
00:32:01,620 --> 00:32:03,659
The owner is my friend. I'm just helping him out.

413
00:32:03,659 --> 00:32:04,781
Hurry up!

414
00:32:04,781 --> 00:32:06,140
Coming.

415
00:32:06,140 --> 00:32:07,698
Eat without me.

416
00:32:36,319 --> 00:32:38,100
Hurry up! I still have to make other deliveries.

417
00:32:38,100 --> 00:32:39,756
I know.

418
00:33:55,722 --> 00:34:01,770
♫ I know the direction of dawn ♫

419
00:34:01,770 --> 00:34:09,035
♫ It's right in front of me, waiting for me to shine ♫

420
00:34:09,035 --> 00:34:14,925
♫  The starlight that shines alone the way  ♫

421
00:34:14,925 --> 00:34:21,065
♫ Accompanying me on my adventure, packing my dreams into my heart ♫

422
00:34:21,065 --> 00:34:27,817
♫  I don't fear the rough journey ahead, I will no longer run away  ♫

423
00:34:27,817 --> 00:34:33,457
♫  Maybe I'm not destined for the hardship of this journey  ♫

424
00:34:33,457 --> 00:34:37,270
♫  And chase after the longing in my heart  ♫

425
00:34:37,270 --> 00:34:40,692
♫  Let set sail on our dreams  ♫

426
00:34:40,692 --> 00:34:43,987
♫  Let's not have any regrets in our youth  ♫

427
00:34:43,987 --> 00:34:50,747
♫  Even if you stumble and fall, I'll be by your side  ♫

428
00:34:50,747 --> 00:34:53,958
♫  Let's find the answer through the madness  ♫

429
00:34:53,958 --> 00:34:58,170
♫  Let's have courage to ride the waves and billows  ♫

430
00:34:58,170 --> 00:35:01,990
♫  With my wings, I'll fly us to the future  ♫

431
00:35:01,990 --> 00:35:09,850
♫  And step forward into the future without fear of sorrow  ♫
